{"tid":1101913,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《地獄男爵》爛番茄新鮮度僅10% 口碑仆街慘不忍睹","createTime":"2019-04-11T10:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T10:53:35.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b533a4d970addbeb9fb23f0ec20738b8c9c9d07","tid":1101913,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"新版《地獄男爵》口碑今日已解禁，慘不忍睹，早先我們已經報導了電影在Metacritic上的媒體均分僅為30+，而電影的爛番茄新鮮度同樣不忍直視，截至發稿前，新鮮度僅為10%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3mVBW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3mVBW9.jpg&h=d4048b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新版《地獄男爵》在爛番茄上總共收穫了49個評價，5鮮44爛，口碑大仆街，對比前作更顯慘烈，要知道04和06年的《地獄男爵》分別在爛番茄上的新鮮度高達81%和86%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZpgmoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZpgmoR.jpg&h=c9c8b393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHollywood Reporter的編輯質疑道，到底是誰叫囂著要搞《地獄男爵》的重啟？<br />\n<br />\n  Entertainment Weekly的編輯則表示，很高興看到製作費高昂的電影能拍成R級，但緊接著他又吐槽道《地獄男爵》滿是無聊的CGI噴血和F髒話。<br />\n<br />\n  indieWire的編輯吐槽儘管新版《地獄男爵》試圖為這系列注入新鮮的生命，但最終卻感覺更像是行屍走肉。<br />\n<br />\n  從如今的評價來看，新版《地獄男爵》的口碑已然崩壞，不知道最終票房能否挽回尊嚴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0pLZaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0pLZaE.jpg&h=91088ddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50385631fb945c963c40888054328b79ce8d0d29","tid":1101913,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"原來上左,但無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d303a371183339d74eacdbee888ac9aca0c8fa8","tid":1101913,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港好似要6月"},{"pid":"81174c393f5fc16843ccd17951bdbccfab62464e","tid":1101913,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"個trailer 見到截圖已經唔想click入去睇"},{"pid":"275e8852b56e79035072e49cb6ac15cb85bd80a0","tid":1101913,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZsBO4b3tyZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZsBO4b3tyZg&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=665187d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZsBO4b3tyZg</a><br />\n有生化系列女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfa0f05b925bab8265ac1c1af6dd00fef809b66","tid":1101913,"uid":129278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"見到男女主角變左己經唔想睇"}]}